    "title": "0.8.2rc rescans wallet on startup even if wallet was just created",
    "body": "Starting the client without a wallet.dat in the directory and generating one causes the client to spend a few minutes rescanning the blockchain (blockchain already downloaded). The chances of generating a key which is already used is so low, why waste time doing this?\n",
